{"tid":1741153,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老細話聖誕之後再係咁嘅話就會執笠止血","createTime":"2019-11-20T08:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T17:54:06.000Z","uid":254923,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9fe59957ccae7ea16b8f7716f799a988a5ee0a","tid":1741153,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"小弟返緊一間貨倉<br />\n細倉仔費時自爆。每年最旺季就係聖誕同埋新年期間呢幾個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老細話睇個勢聖誕之前都搞唔掂，新年更加唔使講。所以諗住聖誕節後提早止血。叫我地有定心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其呢兩個幾月示威升級之後真係好難捱。<br />\n都有同老細傾過下條數係點嘅，真係不敢想像而家尖沙咀嗰啲鋪頭過緊啲咩日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟有唔少人同我一樣新年之前要搵工了。<br />\n可能距離運輸同零售業蕭條不遠了<br />\n<br />\n利申：今日都遲咗個半鐘返工，有做錄音師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49674a90aaf48ad9914a98081ae1e90ac2fb701c","tid":1741153,"uid":254923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"如果兩個月搵唔到工嘅話我會即刻拎仲援<br />\n係咁先。"},{"pid":"c0d6fd2d7126c619d7d40dc8beff0f4b7622cbd4","tid":1741153,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"有冇手足同我一樣差唔多失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e68a3c324aead5b8fc675b920f7d31811a6259","tid":1741153,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"我係咪開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11740232d11eb6b621eb7a9ac1011f97cb18771d","tid":1741153,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38146d0bff6e9f77f60f1e2639b5211658c3148","tid":1741153,"uid":111576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬手足，全香港一齊搞黃色經濟圈，養起自己人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c92fa3ebbc7890971ef5efd64ea8955cdba975","tid":1741153,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38146d0bff6e9f77f60f1e2639b5211658c3148","tid":1741153,"uid":111576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬手足，全香港一齊搞黃色經濟圈，養起自己人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"不了，藍老細"},{"pid":"eee6a9598463e3b6625d445f48432aac825a2e1d","tid":1741153,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:49:48.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n間公司應該真係執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇緊要啦 工再搵過好閒姐"},{"pid":"8f36f3beb58815bf53bb9652062264ca5b190a8a","tid":1741153,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c92fa3ebbc7890971ef5efd64ea8955cdba975","tid":1741153,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38146d0bff6e9f77f60f1e2639b5211658c3148","tid":1741153,"uid":111576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬手足，全香港一齊搞黃色經濟圈，養起自己人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"不了，藍老細"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"多唔多藍同事？"},{"pid":"7acba1afc9215999054384a22ae6ed71f99c0f80","tid":1741153,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:54:06.000Z","msg":"水靜河飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}